data.description: Gorgeous 4 bedroom 4.5 bath with a 3 car garage located in the exclusive Preserve of Mission Valley nestled on 1.32 acre lot that backs up tp a greenbelt. The property features include 4 bedrooms each with their own bathroom a study/office a formal dining are with a separate lining space that has custom floor to ceiling windows that provide an indoor-outdoor experience with an oversized covered patio that has a fireplace and outdoor kitchen. This open floorpan is pre plumbed for a pool also has a game room and media room great for entertainment. Come experience Luxury
